Package: rtic
Type: Package
Title: Provides database interface, analytical calculations, and report writing
  functions for DTC
Version: 0.1.0
Author: Alejandro Sotolongo
Maintainer: Alejandro Sotolongo <asotolongo@diversifiedtrust.com>
Description: rtic is organized around three main objects: Database, Portfolio,
    and Reporter. Database contains methods to download from various data sources 
    and read / write to the DTC database in S3. Portfolio helps organize data
    into investment portfolios and contains methods to run risk / return 
    analytics. Reporter takes Portfolio objects as inputs and manipulates them
    to write common report charts / tables.
License: TBD
Encoding: UTF-8
LazyData: true
Depends: xts, lubridate, timeDate, arrow, dplyr, tidyr, R6, httr, jsonlite, 
    xml2, XML, rvest, curl, ggplot2, ggrepel, slider, reticulate, officer, 
    flextable, allocatoR
RoxygenNote: 7.3.2
